### GraphQL Server Test

### 1. Alle Posts abrufen
POST http://localhost:3000/api/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "{ posts { id title slug excerpt published } }"
}

###

### 2. Einzelner Post nach Slug
POST http://localhost:3000/api/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "{ post(slug: \"getting-started-nextjs\") { id title content comments { id author content } } }"
}

###

### 3. Kommentare zu einem Post
POST http://localhost:3000/api/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "{ comments(postId: 1) { id author content createdAt } }"
}

###
